main event: Unidentified flying objects were observed in Los Angeles, California on September 12, 1960, traveling at approximately 1200 mph and ascending vertically before disappearing into the overcast.
interesting points: The sighting involved approximately 6 objects,Each object was described as moving rapidly and then disappearing,The witness was unidentified, but the report was part of Project Blue Book,No conclusions or evaluations were made in the report,The objects were reported to be going vertically, showing unusual movement patterns.
